text:
@kamalaharris write about how exhausting the fight against brett kavanaugh’s supreme court nomination is and the necessity of keeping up the fight. 
this is a critical fight that selects someone in the highest office of judgment, for life, after he is selected. hell yeah! hold off on this. 
for ☝🏾 bill cosby was just sentenced to jail for similar allegations... the skin tone is making me question the urgency, validity, and the interest of this nomination. nope! naw! nawl! helltodanawnawnaw 👎🏾 #inmyopinion #metoo #issawrap #gabbyvalentinonews #gabbyvalentinoviews #blacklivesmatter do you know how many #blacklives we will lose to prison, war on the drugs, unconvicted police murders, miseducation of the black person... i don’t trust the voter (congress) and the one they voted for (brett) so that’s for 5 thousand million (in my first grade number)🤷🏽‍♀️

